      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im prepping for my ethics seminar next week and we have to debate affirmative action. i need to play devil's advocate for the opposing side. can you help me put together a really strong, persuasive argument against it? like, focus on the meritocracy angle and why race-based policies might actually be unfair or undermine individual achievement.",
